        <div class="row align-items-center g-5 mb-5">
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <div class="section-badge">About Us</div>
                <h2 class="section-title text-dark">Dedicated to Optical Excellence Since 2018</h2>
                <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">Smart Eye Clinic began with a simple but profound mission: to deliver world-class ophthalmic care with a compassionate, patient-centered approach. Over the years, we have grown into a leading optical health network, serving thousands of families with standard diagnostic screenings, complex refractive procedures, and premium vitreoretinal surgeries.</p>
                <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">We believe that clear vision is a fundamental right. That is why our modern facility is equipped with state-of-the-art diagnostic imaging, advanced surgical suites, and staffed by board-certified ophthalmologists dedicated to clinical leadership and educational research.</p>
            </div>
